Coin Score system:
> 0.5	Good BUY strength
> 0.10	Strong BUY confidence
< -0.5	Good SELL strength
< -0.10	Strong SELL confidence
Between -0.4 to 0.4	Weak/sideways signals

To use discord functions use /tradepanel

## [3.1.1] - 2025-05-04
### Added 
- Dynamic position sizing.
- Risk % values.
- New score system that integrates average volatility.

### Changed
- PNL now calculated based of position size and profit goal.
- Retweak of coin score system as too high scores being printed.
- Removed some redundances in the code.
